{
  "description": "Canonical single-node unit/type TCL surface for valkey-rs conformance. Consumed by harness/oracle/safe-survey.py. The deny-tag set is NOT duplicated here: it is resolved from tcl-survey.py's DENY_TAG_PROFILES[profile] so there is one source of truth for tags (the drift that undercounted ~2,445 vs the official ~3,010 on 2026-05-26 was a hardcoded deny set).",
